Ministry Of Sound - Chilled House Classics (2013) 

               House, Club, Vocal, Funky | Ministry of Sound UK

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013 | 03:56:10 | 541 Mb



60 of the best laid back house classics to fill your summer including 'So Good To Me' from Chris Malinchak the Ibiza anthem 'Love Story' from Layo & Bushwacka plus recent hits from Florence + The Machine, Disclosure and Jessie Ware, not forgetting the huge number one record from Duke Dumont ft. A*M*E 'Need You 100%' remixed disco style by BBC Radio One's Skream. Truly the very best... Chilled House Classics! Welcome to MoSTV, the home of new dance music! From bedroom producers to international hitmakers, official videos from the biggest artists, curated playlists from our favourite DJs to the hottest compilations across all genres.
